Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.78,0:01:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}下一條新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.28,0:01:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}預定於上海和平國際會議場召開為期兩天的反恐國際合作會議…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.23,0:01:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 大澤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.12,0:01:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道你鬧什麼彆扭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.29,0:01:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但也沒必要不讓人進門吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.75,0:01:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我換衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.16,0:01:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你換的太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.48,0:01:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經一點了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.59,0:01:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我換的是宫廷禮服
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.35,0:01:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.48,0:02:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}各國首腦自昨天起陸續抵達浦東國際機場…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.86,0:02:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南是個普通的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.14,0:02:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論她有著怎樣的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.24,0:02:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論她過著怎樣的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.49,0:02:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這 只是我在自欺欺人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.20,0:02:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時 迦南她…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.40,0:02:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本不是普通的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.83,0:02:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.92,0:02:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又要失去什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.63,0:03:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏姆 來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.95,0:03:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.44,0:03:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下面還沒看過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用勉強自己去看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.91,0:03:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不該看的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.64,0:03:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不用看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,燃燒著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.04,0:03:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,青色的火焰 燃燒著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.80,0:03:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.05,0:03:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.95,0:03:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不用回答
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.22,0:03:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你從今以後…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要猶豫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,注意壓槍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與多名敵人槍戰時
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向最接近的敵人連射兩發
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算沒有命中 也要以腳趾為軸轉身
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊下一個敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.85,0:04:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別讓對方近身
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,槍的性能是固定的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.55,0:04:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,槍械會使戰士的能力平均化
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進一步講
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.24,0:04:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若不選擇符合當前水平的槍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.48,0:04:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會被第一個淘汰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最先要記住的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.95,0:04:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是手裡的武器…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.64,0:04:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}我喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.02,0:04:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡槍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.83,0:04:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為它沒有顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太陽是青色的 我討厭它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.51,0:04:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是憎恨的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:05:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡有青色的氣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.09,0:05:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡就肯定有敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這性能超乎想像了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.97,0:05:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.37,0:05:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.73,0:05:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是什麼顏色的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.40,0:05:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏姆的顏色…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是淡咖啡色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,淡咖啡色？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.92,0:05:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一週不洗澡的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.82,0:05:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任誰都能看出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想失去…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.92,0:05:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這點疼都忍不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.05,0:05:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖說還是個新人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.35,0:05:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你已經經歷多少戰場了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:05:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該疼時還是會疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.87,0:06:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要勉強自己做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.06,0:06:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是家人的 標誌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.98,0:06:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望之地嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.52,0:06:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不想再失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.61,0:06:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因誰而失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.00,0:06:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏姆！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.75,0:06:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.37,0:06:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底叫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾法鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.49,0:07:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒能成為你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.35,0:07:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨處可見的恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.54,0:07:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還在想著復仇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.45,0:07:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,記住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冤冤相報沒有任何意義
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.45,0:07:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須用義務對抗仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否則無法得到救贖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仇恨毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.34,0:07:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.41,0:07:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我全都知道 夏姆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.15,0:07:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經不想再失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.98,0:07:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 大澤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.48,0:07:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也該給我開門…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.80,0:08:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 不換宫廷禮服了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.97,0:08:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來是放棄打扮了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.91,0:08:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來 出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.74,0:08:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主編教過我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.04,0:08:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討好女人要先討好她的肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.71,0:08:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有這麼簡單呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.65,0:08:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說的不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.45,0:08:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女人心 海底針啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老兄 這樣可沒法抓住奈奈的芳心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不想抓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.21,0:08:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩年前 所有村民都突然失蹤了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.92,0:08:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公安部想掩蓋這個事實
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.65,0:08:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼反恐國際會議啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.78,0:08:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能忘記消失的村莊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.99,0:08:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能容許公安部為所欲為！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蠻有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.67,0:09:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可不像NGO的作風呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.45,0:09:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算演那種猴戲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.96,0:09:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CIA的人也不會去看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得好像事不關己一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.20,0:09:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 與我無關
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.63,0:09:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不打算收下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.91,0:09:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所謂報酬 只有立功的人才有資格收
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也可以看成是將來立功的訂金啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.53,0:09:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我將來只會變成日式夜店的色老頭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.51,0:09:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要抹殺過去？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.95,0:09:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像你抹殺的村莊一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之既然失敗了 我就不能收
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.42,0:09:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個愚者過好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你心中盛開的花
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.88,0:09:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用這個給她買條項鍊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.54,0:09:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:09:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必了 我會在床上取悅她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾為誰而失去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又將為誰而失去…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.18,0:10:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.86,0:10:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.35,0:10:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.94,0:10:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我們喝水就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身心融為一體
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:11:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然會產生如此和諧的效果
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.65,0:11:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你想說蟹黄蟹肉很對味
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.91,0:11:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但也太詩意了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.39,0:11:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很好吃嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人好少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.47,0:11:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為是淡季嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.07,0:11:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上海秋季才產蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.37,0:11:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還能更好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.37,0:11:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在都是養殖的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.18,0:11:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差距沒這麼大…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.17,0:11:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.40,0:11:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實先生不記得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.56,0:11:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在很多地方打過工…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確眼熟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.24,0:11:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但她是個貧乳來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她打了幾份工啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.16,0:11:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這個國家貧乳…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.59,0:11:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 貧富差距比較大嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在想什麼是普通的女孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.16,0:12:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.87,0:12:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,充滿自信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.33,0:12:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,僅憑那份存在感就能壓服眾人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.56,0:12:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這才是我的姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梁琪大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梁琪大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.14,0:12:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這種情況之下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.09,0:12:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,值此NBCR
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.31,0:12:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反恐國際合作會議在上海召開之際
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:12:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能被主辦國中國選為警備合作對象
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我們大太公司無上的榮幸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.39,0:13:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那位女士是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.69,0:13:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是大太公司的大股東
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.33,0:13:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是原中東著名王侯的獨生女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.53,0:13:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.76,0:13:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,氣質果然不同凡響
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.55,0:13:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.18,0:13:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回去呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.92,0:13:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想去散散步
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.18,0:13:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,散步？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.63,0:13:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.11,0:13:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡可不是日本…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.24,0:13:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和你的朋友一模一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.38,0:13:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 盡量不要往暗處走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.86,0:13:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千萬不能去上海站北邊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,武器… 沒有是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.32,0:13:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帶上相機
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:13:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少可以拿閃光燈閃人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.16,0:13:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}迦南…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 千晶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.06,0:14:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到符合標誌的團體了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.05,0:14:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 畫質太差了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.90,0:14:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用數位相機拍的底片…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.63,0:14:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但主編說了些有趣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.43,0:14:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說比起標誌 更像凸起的血管
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.24,0:14:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,血管…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.28,0:14:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,御法川！ 偷什麼懶呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.90,0:14:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追加採訪！ 馬上…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.07,0:14:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,血管以相同的形狀浮現…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.80,0:14:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 吵醒你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.16,0:15:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你好好高興一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.64,0:15:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南… 見面又能怎怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.34,0:15:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為我害怕了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.14,0:16:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為我傷害了她？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.33,0:16:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.03,0:16:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.88,0:16:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每當我遇險時 迦南都會來救我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫非這次也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我端起相機的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.05,0:16:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為我遇到了迦南
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.23,0:17:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了正視那些未知的事物 曾被自己無視的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.02,0:17:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了去了解迦南
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.35,0:17:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在耍什麼脾氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她之所以開槍 全是為了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.71,0:17:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我卻一心想要逃避罪惡感
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從心底某處責備著迦南
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.37,0:17:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord2}哎 不允許拍 不允許拍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord2}這不能給人看到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.70,0:17:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要緊的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要用自己雙眼去看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.96,0:17:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用自己的心去判斷！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會對真相視而不見的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord2}我要把那玩意塞進你耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.03,0:17:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord2}打得你滿地找牙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.99,0:17:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord2}看你還廢話不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.26,0:17:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我不會逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为大澤瑪麗亞是迦南的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord2}不是說了嗎 不許拍…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.95,0:17:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是迦南的… 好朋友啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.56,0:17:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.60,0:17:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呀呀呀 讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.08,0:17:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打工拖了一會兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.97,0:17:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord2}對不起對不起 謝謝 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.16,0:18:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等… 等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.30,0:18:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.68,0:18:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.98,0:18:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏天吃毛蟹的日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡可不是你的祖國
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.28,0:18:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.45,0:18:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一帶很亂 不要再接近了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.10,0:18:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大澤瑪麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.80,0:18:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大澤瑪麗亞 是我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.37,0:18:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.77,0:18:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你談談
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的事 迦南的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.63,0:18:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都想知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.92,0:18:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發現一個世界奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.84,0:19:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可喜可賀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.83,0:19:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人說過
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,體驗過恐懼的人 不會為仇恨所動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.64,0:19:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南和你我不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.30,0:19:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可喜可賀？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.75,0:19:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和我墮落到同一水平線上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.64,0:19:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的眼神裡充滿了仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.59,0:19:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.46,0:19:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的反應變慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時的你 沒有這麼弱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.82,0:20:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算在我殺了夏姆之後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.75,0:20:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.99,0:20:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為憎恨而戰的感覺如何啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.65,0:20:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像泥潭一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.77,0:20:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越是掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.48,0:20:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越會陷入那無盡的黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.81,0:20:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我忍過了那份屈辱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.49,0:20:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經爬上岸了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.85,0:20:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得好聽…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.14,0:20:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你看個證據吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.29,0:21:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還能成長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.74,0:21:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會殺你
